subSubSection.paragraph:
Description. Head.
Fastigium of the vertex in dorsal view blunt, wider and more prominent than antennal scape (
Figs. 14E, H
; 
19D
). In frontal view, like an inverted triangle but not heart-shaped (
Fig. 14C, D
); in lateral view, slightly elevated and protruding (
Figs. 14G
; 
19C
).

